## jstack

Skills at: `~/.claude/skills/jstack/`
Project state: `.claude/PROJECT.md`
Decisions: `DECISIONS.md`

**At the start of each session:** read `.claude/PROJECT.md` and report the state without the dev having to ask. Suggest the next command.

**Available skills:**
- `/status` — resume the project, see where I am
- `/think` — define the problem before planning
- `/plan` — technical plan with diagrams and test matrix
- `/review` — staff engineer code review
- `/qa` — QA with Playwright in a real browser
- `/debug` — systematic root cause analysis
- `/ship` — sync, tests, push and PR
- `/docs-update` — update docs after shipping
- `/retro` — weekly retrospective with real metrics
- `/careful` — warn before destructive commands
- `/freeze [dir]` — restrict edits to one directory
- `/unfreeze` — deactivate freeze

